item.title: CVE-2023-39980|2024-09-27T16:02:36.484Z -- moxa -- mxsecurity%20series
item.description: A vulnerability that allows the unauthorized disclosure of authenticated information has been identified in MXsecurity versions prior to v1.0.1. This vulnerability arises when special elements are not neutralized correctly, allowing remote attackers to alter SQL commands.
